===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Ethan (Masters)}}
Ethan, who is based on the [[player character]], forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Cyndaquil}} and its evolved forms {{p|Quilava}} and {{p|Typhlosion}}, along with {{p|Lugia}}, {{p|Ho-Oh}}, and {{p|Raikou}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Ethan became a playable sync pair on January 15, 2020.

Ethan has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]] and the [[villain arc]]. Unlike in {{game|Crystal}}, both Ethan and {{mas|Kris}} coexist in the same game.

